FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783711191
OL,3,CYet another heat record broken as
OL,4,Ctemperatures continue to soar
OL,6,FJamie Stideford said his team can't
OL,7,Fget units on customers' walls fast
OL,8,Fenough, and they've never known
OL,9,Fanything like it.
OL,11,F"The main issue at the moment is
OL,12,Fstock. All the suppliers are
OL,13,Fstruggling with stock at the moment.
OL,15,F"We're looking at August to take on
OL,16,Fnew installs, minimum. We're fully
OL,17,Fbooked up till the middle or end of
OL,18,FSeptember."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
