CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783711191
OL,3,CYet another heat record broken as
OL,4,Ctemperatures continue to soar
OL,6,FEarly harvests have also begun for
OL,7,Fwheat and oilseed rape at the Leckford
OL,8,FEstate in Hampshire.
OL,10,FTraditionally, harvest season runs
OL,11,Ffrom late July through to October in
OL,12,Fthe UK.
OL,14,FDave Miles, farm manager at the
OL,15,FLeckford Estate, said: "The record-
OL,16,Fbreaking heat we are experiencing is a
OL,17,Fstark wake-up call to our changing
OL,18,Fclimate."
